  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Kill The Topulus</strong> is a simple first-person shooter. Get ready to fight against the fearsome Topulus: giant humanoid mice that not only challenge you with their unpredictable teleportation, but will also insult and laugh at you as they try to eliminate you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2583280/extras/6437373eb69fec361eb0e82113a8d81a.poster.avif?t=1755370683\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2583280/extras/6437373eb69fec361eb0e82113a8d81a.webm?t=1755370683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2583280/extras/6437373eb69fec361eb0e82113a8d81a.mp4?t=1755370683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Arm yourself and take on the challenge</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grab your trusty laser gun and get ready to shoot with precision and timing. In each level, your main objective is simple but challenging: <strong>shoot the Topulus before they shoot you</strong>. Every second counts, a single hesitation can make the difference between success and failure.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Challenges and Scores</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With an average duration of about <strong>40 minutes</strong> to complete the game, the focus is on achievements and scores, each level offers <strong>secondary challenges</strong> that will test your skills, such as:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Finish a level within a time limit.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Avoid using heals or checkpoints.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defeat a certain number of enemies without taking damage.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get multipliers and high scores.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After completing the game once, you will unlock the mode that allows you to replay each level individually, facing the secondary challenges and competing for <strong>the highest score</strong> both globally and for each level. Will you be able to climb the leaderboards and prove that you are the best?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2583280/extras/a89e7abb0ce5c572b98d662e22b6e2ef.poster.avif?t=1755370683\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2583280/extras/a89e7abb0ce5c572b98d662e22b6e2ef.webm?t=1755370683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2583280/extras/a89e7abb0ce5c572b98d662e22b6e2ef.mp4?t=1755370683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Main Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple and intuitive gameplay, but requiring skill and reflexes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Online leaderboards to compete with other players around the world.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Secondary challenges for each level that offer replayability.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Can you become the Master of Topulus?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on the challenge, perfect your strategy and aim for the highest score. The Topulus are ready... and you?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2583280/extras/319753ab75361dfbff1f95bd22916fde.poster.avif?t=1755370683\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2583280/extras/319753ab75361dfbff1f95bd22916fde.webm?t=1755370683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2583280/extras/319753ab75361dfbff1f95bd22916fde.mp4?t=1755370683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Kill The Topulus</strong> is a simple first-person shooter. Get ready to fight against the fearsome Topulus: giant humanoid mice that not only challenge you with their unpredictable teleportation, but will also insult and laugh at you as they try to eliminate you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2583280/extras/6437373eb69fec361eb0e82113a8d81a.poster.avif?t=1755370683\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2583280/extras/6437373eb69fec361eb0e82113a8d81a.webm?t=1755370683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2583280/extras/6437373eb69fec361eb0e82113a8d81a.mp4?t=1755370683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Arm yourself and take on the challenge</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grab your trusty laser gun and get ready to shoot with precision and timing. In each level, your main objective is simple but challenging: <strong>shoot the Topulus before they shoot you</strong>. Every second counts, a single hesitation can make the difference between success and failure.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Challenges and Scores</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With an average duration of about <strong>40 minutes</strong> to complete the game, the focus is on achievements and scores, each level offers <strong>secondary challenges</strong> that will test your skills, such as:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Finish a level within a time limit.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Avoid using heals or checkpoints.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defeat a certain number of enemies without taking damage.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get multipliers and high scores.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After completing the game once, you will unlock the mode that allows you to replay each level individually, facing the secondary challenges and competing for <strong>the highest score</strong> both globally and for each level. Will you be able to climb the leaderboards and prove that you are the best?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2583280/extras/a89e7abb0ce5c572b98d662e22b6e2ef.poster.avif?t=1755370683\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2583280/extras/a89e7abb0ce5c572b98d662e22b6e2ef.webm?t=1755370683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2583280/extras/a89e7abb0ce5c572b98d662e22b6e2ef.mp4?t=1755370683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Main Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple and intuitive gameplay, but requiring skill and reflexes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Online leaderboards to compete with other players around the world.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Secondary challenges for each level that offer replayability.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Can you become the Master of Topulus?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on the challenge, perfect your strategy and aim for the highest score. The Topulus are ready... and you?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2583280/extras/319753ab75361dfbff1f95bd22916fde.poster.avif?t=1755370683\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2583280/extras/319753ab75361dfbff1f95bd22916fde.webm?t=1755370683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2583280/extras/319753ab75361dfbff1f95bd22916fde.mp4?t=1755370683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
